'''2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员'''是[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]]于2017年12月5日因[[俄罗斯体育禁药|俄罗斯禁药问题]]宣布撤销[[俄罗斯奥林匹克委员会|该国奥林匹克委员会]]会员资格后，为让符合相应资格且未曾服用禁药的俄罗斯运动员能够参赛而特别设立的[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会]]代表团。这是俄罗斯时隔26年再度以独立参赛者身份参加冬季奥运（上一次是以独联体身份参赛）<ref name="guardian20180226">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/feb/26/russia-rues-ban-as-oars-deliver-nations-worst-winter-olympics-gold-medal-haul|title=Russia rues ban as OARs deliver nation's worst Winter Olympics gold medal haul|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|date=2018-02-26|accessdate=2018-03-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610215331/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/feb/26/russia-rues-ban-as-oars-deliver-nations-worst-winter-olympics-gold-medal-haul|archivedate=2018-06-10|deadurl=no}}</ref>。俄罗斯运动员在本届冬奥以[[奥林匹克旗帜|奥林匹克旗帜]]参赛，若该国选手获得金牌，颁奖仪式会播放[[奥林匹克会歌|奥林匹克会歌]]<ref name="washingtonpost20171206">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/kidspost/russia-banned-from-competing-in-2018-olympics/2017/12/06/163c763a-d5ed-11e7-95bf-df7c19270879_story.html|title=Russia banned from competing in 2018 Olympics|publisher=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|date=2017-12-06|accessdate=2018-03-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180313153434/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/kidspost/russia-banned-from-competing-in-2018-olympics/2017/12/06/163c763a-d5ed-11e7-95bf-df7c19270879_story.html|archivedate=2018-03-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>。同时该国运动员在该届冬奥所获奖牌将不计入俄罗斯队历届冬奥所获总奖牌数<ref name="nytimes20171205">{{cite web |date=2017-12-05 |title=Russia Banned From Winter Olympics by I.O.C. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/05/sports/olympics/ioc-russia-winter-olympics.html |work=The New York Times |access-date=2017-12-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227215249/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/05/sports/olympics/ioc-russia-winter-olympics.html |archivedate=2018-02-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2018年1月底，国际奥委会公布了获得冬奥资格的169名俄罗斯籍运动员的名单，当中的大多数运动员都未参加过往届冬奥。<ref name="finalroster">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/25/sports/olympics/russia-doping.html|title=Russia Is Barred From Winter Olympics. Russia Is Sending 169 Athletes to Winter Olympics|date=2018-01-25|publisher=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2018-02-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180325222518/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/25/sports/olympics/russia-doping.html|archivedate=2018-03-25|deadurl=no}}</ref>俄罗斯奥委会称这些入选名单的运动员将自行决定是否参赛，最终有一人选择退赛<ref name="olgagraf">{{cite news|url=https://www.gazeta.ru/sport/2018/01/30/a_11630341.shtml|script-title=ru:Вежливый отказ: Граф не поедет на Олимпиаду|date=2018-01-20|publisher={{lang|ru|[[俄罗斯报|Российская газета]]}}|accessdate=2018-02-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206131541/https://www.gazeta.ru/sport/2018/01/30/a_11630341.shtml|archivedate=2018-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，至此共有168名运动员代表俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员参赛<ref name="number168">{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/2018/02/07/russian-olympians-adapt-to-life-in-a-neutral-uniform/110179628/|title=Russian Olympians adapt to life in a neutral uniform|publisher=[[今日美国|USA Today]]|date=2018-02-07|accessdate=2018-03-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180313103703/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/2018/02/07/russian-olympians-adapt-to-life-in-a-neutral-uniform/110179628/|archivedate=2018-03-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员在该届冬奥共获得包括2金6银9铜在内的共17枚奖牌，位居奖牌榜第13名，仅有的两枚金牌分别来自于花样滑冰女子单人滑和男子冰球项目。尽管该队金牌数以及奖牌榜排名均差过[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]代表团首次参加冬奥以来的最差纪录，但该队在该届冬奥所获奖牌总数依然超过了俄罗斯代表团在[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2010年温哥华冬奥会]]以及[[2002年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2002年盐湖城冬奥会]]上所获得的奖牌数。<ref name="guardian20180226"/>

该届冬奥期间共有两例禁药违规与俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员有关。两例分别为参加混合双人冰壶项目的{{le|亚历山大·克鲁舍利尼茨基|Alexander Krushelnitskiy}}以及参加女子双人雪车项目的{{le|娜杰日达·谢尔盖耶娃|Nadezhda Sergeeva}}，两人各自所参加项目的成绩都被取消<ref name="curlingdoping">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/feb/22/russian-curler-alexander-krushelnitsky-stripped-of-winter-olympics-medal-after-admitting-doping|title=Russian curler stripped of Winter Olympics medal after admitting doping|date=2018-02-22|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|access-date=2018-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180306115652/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/feb/22/russian-curler-alexander-krushelnitsky-stripped-of-winter-olympics-medal-after-admitting-doping|archivedate=2018-03-06|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="bobsleighdoping">{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-2018-doping/olympics-russian-bobsledder-sergeeva-admits-anti-doping-violation-cas-idUSKCN1G808W|title=Russian bobsledder Sergeeva admits anti-doping violation: CAS|date=2018-02-24|accessdate=2018-02-24|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180312200402/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-2018-doping/olympics-russian-bobsledder-sergeeva-admits-anti-doping-violation-cas-idUSKCN1G808W|archivedate=2018-03-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>。国际奥委会以这两例禁药案例为由决定不在该届冬奥闭幕式期间恢复俄罗斯奥委会的会员资格<ref name="np20180224">{{cite web|url=http://nationalpost.com/sports/olympics/ioc-recommends-upholding-ban-of-russia-through-winter-games|title=No Russia flag in closing ceremonies: IOC votes to uphold doping ban|publisher=National Post|date=2018-02-24|accessdate=2018-03-13|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180612110358/http://nationalpost.com/sports/olympics/ioc-recommends-upholding-ban-of-russia-through-winter-games|archivedate=2018-06-12|deadurl=no|df=}}</ref>。后来由于对剩余药检样本的检查结束后未再出现与俄罗斯奥运选手相关的禁药案例，国际奥委会于2018年2月28日恢复俄罗斯奥委会的会员资格<ref name="ioc20180228">{{Cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-statement-2018-02-28|title=IOC statement|access-date=2018-02-28|work=IOC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180312200402/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-statement-2018-02-28|archivedate=2018-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
===俄罗斯禁药丑闻===
2016年5月，俄罗斯反禁药机构实验室前负责人[[格里戈里·罗琴科夫|格里戈里·罗琴科夫]]向媒体爆料称，该国有多名运动员曾在[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会|索契冬奥会]]期间服用禁药，而该国的反兴奋剂实验室也曾在赛事举办期间使用包括调换尿液样本在内的各种手段帮助运动员逃避处罚<ref name="nyt2">{{cite web |title=Mystery in Sochi Doping Case Lies With Tamper-Proof Bottle |authors=REBECCA R. RUIZ and MICHAEL SCHWIRTZ |publisher=[[纽约时报|New York Times]] |date=2016-05-13 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/13/sports/russia-doping-sochi-olympics-2014.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2016-05-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160513150111/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/13/sports/russia-doping-sochi-olympics-2014.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2016-05-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。当时正值[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2016年里约夏奥]]举办之际，国际奥委会主席巴赫对此回应称如果此事属实，俄罗斯全队的奥运参赛资格可能会被剥夺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/19/sports/olympics/doping-ioc-president-russia-could-be-barred.html?_r=0 |title=I.O.C. President Says Russian Federations Could Be Barred |publisher=The New York Times |date=2016-05-19 |accessdate=2016-06-22 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hczADase?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/19/sports/olympics/doping-ioc-president-russia-could-be-barred.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2016-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

同年7月18日，[[世界反运动禁药组织|世界反运动禁药组织]]公布了由Richard McLaren所作的报告，该报告称俄羅斯政府和聯邦安全局有計畫支持選手使用禁藥并使用一些手段帮助运动员逃避处罚。<ref name=wada20160718>{{cite news|title=Wada: Russian government oversaw widespread doping – as it happened|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2016/jul/18/wada-mclaren-report-russia-sochi-2014-doping-live|accessdate=2016-07-18|agency=The Guardian|date=2016-07-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204061222/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2016/jul/18/wada-mclaren-report-russia-sochi-2014-doping-live|archivedate=2017-12-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>12月9日，McLaren发布了报告的第二部分，根据这份报告，2011年至2015年间共有超过1000名俄罗斯运动员受益于国家支持的兴奋剂体系，涉及多个奥运及-{zh-hans:残奥;zh-hant:殘奧;zh-tw:帕運;}-项目<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/09/sports/russia-doping-mclaren-report.html |title= Russia's Doping Program Laid Bare by Extensive Evidence in Report |work= The New York Times |first= Rebecca R. |last= Ruiz |date= 2016-12-09 |accessdate= 2016-12-09 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20180302201732/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/09/sports/russia-doping-mclaren-report.html |archivedate= 2018-03-02 |deadurl= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2016/dec/09/mclaren-report-into-doping-in-sport-part-two-live |title= McLaren report: more than 1,000 Russian athletes involved in doping conspiracy |work= The Guardian |first= Lawrence |last= Ostlere |date= 2016-12-09 |accessdate= 2016-12-09 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20171130123449/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2016/dec/09/mclaren-report-into-doping-in-sport-part-two-live |archivedate= 2017-11-30 |deadurl= no }}</ref>。该报告发布后，国际奥委会宣布将对所有参加过2014年索契冬奥的俄罗斯运动员的尿液样本进行重新检查，并对28名参加过2014年索契冬奥的俄罗斯运动员展开调查<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/statement-of-the-ioc-regarding-the-independent-person-report|title=Statement of the IOC regarding the "Independent Person" report|date=2016-12-09|work=IOC|accessdate=2017-01-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719150112/https://www.olympic.org/news/statement-of-the-ioc-regarding-the-independent-person-report|archivedate=2017-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年11月至2017年12月期间，国际奥委会处罚了43名曾参加2014年索契冬奥俄罗斯运动员<ref name="CAS2018-02">{{cite web|url=http://www.tas-cas.org/fileadmin/user_upload/Media_Release__decision_RUS_IOC_.pdf|title=The Court of Arbitration for Sport (CAS) delivers its decisions in the matter of 39 Russian athletes v/the IOC: 28 appeals upheld, 11 partially upheld|publisher=Court of Arbitration for Sport|accessdate=2018-02-01|date=2018-02-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227214933/http://www.tas-cas.org/fileadmin/user_upload/Media_Release__decision_RUS_IOC_.pdf|archivedate=2018-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并剥夺了该国在该届冬奥所获得的13枚奖牌，同时禁止被处罚的俄罗斯运动员参加2018年及以后进行的冬奥赛事<ref>{{cite web | url=http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2017/11/27/sochi-olympic-medal-standings-russia-medals-stripped-doping/ | title=List of Russia Olympic medals stripped; new Sochi medal standings | publisher=NBC Sports | date=2017-11-27 | accessdate=2017-12-22 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315081432/http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2017/11/27/sochi-olympic-medal-standings-russia-medals-stripped-doping/ | archivedate=2018-03-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。而被国际奥委会列入调查对象的俄罗斯运动员人数也在12月时升至46人<ref>{{cite web|date=2017-12-01|title=IOC sanctions 11 Russian athletes as part of Oswald Commission findings|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-sanctions-11-russian-athletes-as-part-of-oswald-commission-findings|publisher=IOC|accessdate=2017-12-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319233616/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-sanctions-11-russian-athletes-as-part-of-oswald-commission-findings|archivedate=2018-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

俄罗斯方面否认该国存在国家支持的兴奋剂体系，[[俄罗斯总统|该国总统]]普京称国际奥委会受到了来自[[美国|美国]]的压力<ref>{{cite news |date=2017-10-19 |title=Putin says US pressured IOC to ban Russia from Winter Games |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/putin-says-us-pressured-ioc-ban-russia-winter-175151912--oly.html |work=Yahoo Sports |agency=Agence France-Presse |access-date=2017-12-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206160927/https://sports.yahoo.com/putin-says-us-pressured-ioc-ban-russia-winter-175151912--oly.html |archivedate=2017-12-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他还表示美国正在利用此事干涉[[2018年俄罗斯总统选举|2018年俄罗斯总统选举]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/putin-calls-olympics-punishments-sign-u-s-election-meddling-n819561|title=Putin Calls Olympics Punishments a Sign of U.S. Election Meddling|date=2017-11-09|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2017-11-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220172908/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/putin-calls-olympics-punishments-sign-u-s-election-meddling-n819561|archivedate=2018-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===正式处罚===
[[File:Olympic_Athlete_from_Russia_logo_2018.svg|thumb]]
2017年12月5日，国际奥委会宣布将从当日开始撤销俄罗斯奥林匹克委员会的会员资格。未曾服用禁药且符合相应资格的俄罗斯运动员将被允许以“俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员”（{{lang|en|Olympic Athlete from Russia}}，缩写：{{lang|en|OAR}}）的身份参加2018年平昌冬奥<ref name="nytimes20171205"/>。同时，俄罗斯官员被禁止出席2018年平昌冬奥，而与俄罗斯相关的标志（包括[[俄罗斯国旗|国旗]]、[[俄罗斯国徽|国徽]]与[[俄罗斯国歌|国歌]]等）也不允许在冬奥赛场上出现{{notetag|国际奥委会仅禁止俄罗斯相关的标志出现在与运动员相关的地方，并未禁止现场观众在观看冬奥比赛期间携带甚至展示与俄罗斯相关的标志<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/winter-olympics-2018/russian-fans-spurn-stupid-ban-athletes-olympic-games-n847886 | title=Russian fans spurn 'stupid' ban on athletes at Olympic Games | publisher=NBC News | first=Eirk | last=Ortiz | date=2018-02-14 | accessdate=2018-02-14 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315011612/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/winter-olympics-2018/russian-fans-spurn-stupid-ban-athletes-olympic-games-n847886 | archivedate=2018-03-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。<ref name="washingtonpost20171206"/>国际奥委会主席[[托马斯·巴赫|托马斯·巴赫]]称俄罗斯的禁药丑闻是对奥运会以及奥林匹克运动完整性的一次空前攻击，他还称国际奥委会的行动既对这一系统性的操纵实施了处罚，同时又保护了干净的运动员<ref>{{cite web | url=https://themoscowtimes.com/news/ioc-bars-russian-athletes-and-officials-from-winter-olympic-games-59818 | title=IOC Bars Russian Athletes and Officials From Winter Olympic Games | work=The Moscow Times | date=2017-12-05 | accessdate=2017-12-05 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227221154/https://themoscowtimes.com/news/ioc-bars-russian-athletes-and-officials-from-winter-olympic-games-59818 | archivedate=2018-02-27 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在国际奥委会宣布禁止俄罗斯以国家名义参加2018年平昌冬奥后，有俄罗斯官员表示该国的运动员应该放弃参加该届冬奥<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.interfax.ru/sport/590596 |script-title=ru:Жириновский предложил отказаться от участия в Олимпиаде-2018 |publisher=Interfax.ru |date=2017-12-06 |access-date=2017-12-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231011733/http://www.interfax.ru/sport/590596 |archivedate=2017-12-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[车臣共和国|车臣共和国]][[车臣共和国首脑|首脑]][[拉姆赞·卡德罗夫|拉姆赞·卡德罗夫]]称车臣运动员将不被允许以中立旗帜参赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.championat.com/other/news-2972433-kadyrov-ni-odin-chechenskij-sportsmen-ne-budet-vystupat-pod-nejtralnym-flagom.html|script-title=ru:Кадыров: ни один чеченский спортсмен не будет выступать под нейтральным флагом|publisher={{lang|ru|Чемпионат}}|access-date=2017-12-06|date=2017-12-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227214904/https://www.championat.com/other/news-2972433-kadyrov-ni-odin-chechenskij-sportsmen-ne-budet-vystupat-pod-nejtralnym-flagom.html|archivedate=2018-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而俄罗斯总统普京则表示，俄罗斯政府不会阻止愿意参赛的该国运动员以个人身份参加冬奥<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/12/06/sport/russia-doping-2018-winter-olympics-vladimir-putin-pyeongchang/index.html|title=Vladimir Putin won't tell Russian athletes to boycott Winter Olympics|date=2017-12-06|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|access-date=2017-12-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209193804/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/12/06/sport/russia-doping-2018-winter-olympics-vladimir-putin-pyeongchang/index.html|archivedate=2018-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

12月20日，国际奥委会公布了获得批准的俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员队伍的队服以及标志。根据国际奥委会规定，该队队服既不允许俄罗斯国旗中的全部三种颜色同时出现，也不允许使用任何象征俄罗斯的设计元素。标志方面，国际奥委会规定标志上所有文字的字体与大小必须保持一致，同时文字的大小应当与制服和装备相协调。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-s-olympic-athlete-from-russia-implementation-group-releases-guidelines-for-uniforms-accessories-and-equipment|title=IOC's Olympic Athlete from Russia implementation group releases guidelines for uniforms accessories and equipment's|date=2017-12-20|work=IOC|accessdate=2017-12-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323222145/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-s-olympic-athlete-from-russia-implementation-group-releases-guidelines-for-uniforms-accessories-and-equipment|archivedate=2018-03-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在国际奥委会对43名俄罗斯运动员实施处罚后，共有42名运动员向国际体育仲裁院提出上诉。2018年2月1日，国际体育仲裁院决定撤销其中28名运动员的禁赛处罚，并恢复这些运动员的成绩<ref name="CAS2018-02"/>。其后，国际奥委会发表声明称国际体育仲裁院的这一判决并不代表被解除处罚的28名运动员将获邀参加冬奥<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-statement-on-cas-decision|title=IOC Statement on CAS Decision|date=2018-02-01|work=IOC|accessdate=2018-02-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180228002230/http://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-statement-on-cas-decision|archivedate=2018-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

俄罗斯于2018年1月向国际奥委会提交了一份500人的参赛名单，其中有111人被国际奥委会初步移出。根据要求，余下的运动员必须确保自身没有任何的药检阳性记录（包括赛前检查和赛后重检）才能进入正式名单<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/reduced-pool-of-russian-athletes-and-officials-who-can-be-considered-for-invitation-to-pyeongchang-2018-determined|title=Reduced Pool of Russian Athletes and Officials Who Can Be Considered for Invitation to PyeongChang 2018 Determined|date=2018-01-25|work=IOC|accessdate=2018-01-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227215441/https://www.olympic.org/news/reduced-pool-of-russian-athletes-and-officials-who-can-be-considered-for-invitation-to-pyeongchang-2018-determined|archivedate=2018-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经过筛选，国际奥委会于2018年1月底公布了入选俄罗斯奥林匹克阵容的169人名单，名单当中绝大多数运动员都是第一次参加冬奥<ref name="finalroster"/>。名单公布后，俄罗斯奥委会称这些入选名单的运动员将自行决定是否参赛，最终只有速度滑冰选手[[Olga_Graf|Olga Graf]]宣布退赛<ref name="olgagraf"/>，至此共有168名运动员代表俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员队参加该届冬奥<ref name="number168"/>。

===资格恢复===
[[File:Dmitry_Medvedev_with_sportspeople_(2018-02-28).jpg|thumb]]于2018年2月28日与在2018年平昌冬奥期间获得奖牌的俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员合影。]]
俄罗斯被禁赛期间，国际奥委会曾一度考虑在[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会闭幕式|闭幕式]]期间恢复俄罗斯奥委会的会员资格，并允许俄罗斯运动员携带国旗进入闭幕式会场<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1061761/russia-optimistic-ban-will-be-lifted-before-pyeongchang-2018-closing-ceremony-after-bach-meets-with-putin-aide|title=Russia optimistic ban will be lifted before Pyeongchang 2018 Closing Ceremony after Bach meets with Putin aide|publisher=Inside the Games|date=2018-02-21|accessdate=2018-03-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227215706/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1061761/russia-optimistic-ban-will-be-lifted-before-pyeongchang-2018-closing-ceremony-after-bach-meets-with-putin-aide|archivedate=2018-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rt.com/sport/419449-russian-flag-pyeongchang-olympics/|title=Will Russians be allowed to fly the flag at PyeongChang closing ceremony?|publisher=[[今日俄罗斯|Russia Today]]|date=2018-02-21|accessdate=2018-03-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315133933/https://www.rt.com/sport/419449-russian-flag-pyeongchang-olympics/|archivedate=2018-03-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>，据媒体报道，当时仅有少数国际奥委会委员反对这一提议<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-2018-russia/ioc-edges-closer-to-bringing-russia-in-from-the-cold-sources-idUSKCN1G6152|title=IOC edges closer to bringing Russia in from the cold|publisher=Reuters|date=2018-02-22|accessdate=2018-03-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315195858/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-2018-russia/ioc-edges-closer-to-bringing-russia-in-from-the-cold-sources-idUSKCN1G6152|archivedate=2018-03-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。然而在赛事进行期间共发现两例涉及俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员的禁药事件，其中一例为参加混合双人冰壶项目的选手{{le|亚历山大·克鲁舍利尼茨基|Alexander Krushelnitskiy}}，他在一次药检中被查出[[米屈肼|米屈肼]]呈阳性，这导致俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员失去了混合双人冰壶铜牌<ref name="curlingdoping"/>；另一例为女子雪车运动员{{le|娜杰日达·谢尔盖耶娃|Nadezhda Sergeeva}}，她因被查出[[曲美他嗪|曲美他嗪]]呈阳性而被取消成绩<ref name="bobsleighdoping"/>。外界认为，这两例禁药事件将影响国际奥委会关于解除俄罗斯奥委会禁令的决定<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/2018/02/24/confusion-reigns-as-ioc-hedges-on-what-to-do-about-russians/110776304/|title=IOC delays decision on whether to reinstate Russia for closing ceremony at Olympics|publisher=USA Today|date=2018-02-24|accessdate=2018-03-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315135025/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/2018/02/24/confusion-reigns-as-ioc-hedges-on-what-to-do-about-russians/110776304/|archivedate=2018-03-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

闭幕式开始前，国际奥委会决定在闭幕式期间维持对俄罗斯奥委会的禁令，理由是该届冬奥进行期间共发生两例涉及俄罗斯奥林匹克运动员的禁药事件<ref name="np20180224"/>。尽管如此，国际奥委会仍承诺称如果其他166名俄罗斯奥运选手的样本均未发生阳性反应，俄罗斯奥委会的会员资格将在“数日或数周内”被恢复<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20180225-olympics-pyeongchang-ioc-keeps-ban-russia-winter-games-closing-ceremony-doping|title=IOC keeps ban on Russia for Winter Games closing ceremony|publisher=[[法蘭西24|France 24]]|date=2018-02-25|accessdate=2018-03-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315193041/http://www.france24.com/en/20180225-olympics-pyeongchang-ioc-keeps-ban-russia-winter-games-closing-ceremony-doping|archivedate=2018-03-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2月28日，国际奥委会在确认剩余的俄罗斯奥运选手的样本均无异常后，恢复了俄罗斯奥委会的会员资格<ref name="ioc20180228"/>。

